  "message": "fuzz(dtype_parsing): extend corpus with 21 edge-case seeds\n\nAdds coverage for:\n- Explicit byte order markers (>, <, =, |)\n- Float/uint/int/cfloat aliases\n- Shaped dtypes like (2,3)i4\n- Repeated dtype shorthand (3float32)\n- Minimal byte markers (S, U)\n- Various datetime/timedelta units\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
